---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout>
  <section class="space-y-6">
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight">
      Jeff Hidalgo
    </h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-zinc-300">
      Security engineer focused on offensive security and AI/LLM security. Based in NYC.
    </p>
    <p class="text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">
      I'm building toward a career at the intersection of penetration testing and AI security.
      Currently studying for OSCP, running a home lab on Kali, and building tools that solve
      problems I actually run into.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-16 space-y-4">
    <h2 class="text-sm font-mono uppercase tracking-wider text-zinc-500">Recent work</h2>
    <ul class="space-y-4">
      <li class="border border-zinc-800 rounded-lg p-5 hover:border-zinc-700 transition-colors">
        <a href="/projects/scanner" class="block">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-zinc-100">Network Scanner</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400 mt-1">
            Multi-stage Python scanner with PostgreSQL backend and diff reporting.
            Built around the real workflow: baseline → rescan → report-what-changed.
          </p>
        </a>
      </li>
      <li class="border border-zinc-800 rounded-lg p-5 hover:border-zinc-700 transition-colors">
        <a href="/projects/mlb-model" class="block">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-zinc-100">MLB Prediction Model</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400 mt-1">
            Gradient boosting models for player props, trained on FanGraphs data 2023-2025,
            integrated with live odds.
          </p>
        </a>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-16 space-y-2">
    <h2 class="text-sm font-mono uppercase tracking-wider text-zinc-500">Currently studying</h2>
    <p class="text-zinc-300">OSCP · AI/LLM security · Multi-agent pentest tooling</p>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-8 space-y-2">
    <h2 class="text-sm font-mono uppercase tracking-wider text-zinc-500">Certifications</h2>
    <p class="text-zinc-300">A+ · Network+ · Security+</p>
  </section>
</Layout>